I’m calling on you, K State Nation to Get In The Game with me and become a member of @BeTheMatch today. 

Every 3 minutes, someone is diagnosed with a blood cancer like leukemia, which can be cured through a blood stem cell transplant. Thousands of patients each year are waiting for their matching donor to join the registry and say YES when called. 

Text KSTATE18 to 61474 to become a potential blood stem cell donor. It only takes a simple cheek swab (they’ll mail you a swab kit) and you’ll only be called to donate if you are a match for a patient. #GetInTheGame #BeTheMatch

Kansas State’s Will Howard has blossomed into one of the top QB prospects in the 2024 draft.

But coming out of high school, every school passed him over.

Duke, UNC, Syracuse, Pitt, Penn State. The list goes on.

But @will.howard18 had his sights set on playing at a Power 5 program.

So he set out to become Kansas State’s next great QB.

Now Howard’s sights are on the Texas Longhorns, as the Wildcats are gearing up for the biggest game of their season.

In this episode of @nextupwithab opens up about his recruitment, Kansas State’s offense, and...

How he plans to take down Texas.
